OL,3,C'It's a form of corruption': Police
OL,4,Caccused of using position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FNineteen investigations into cases of
OL,8,Fabuse of position for sexual purposes
OL,9,Fby police in Northern Ireland were
OL,10,Fbeing carried out by the Police
OL,11,FOmbudsman at the time of an inspection
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FChief inspector of criminal justice
OL,15,FJacqui Durkin said the total was the
OL,16,Fhighest to date in her report
OL,17,Fexamining how the Office of the Police
OL,18,FOmbudsman for Northern Ireland (OPONI)
OL,19,Fhandles and investigates abuse of
OL,20,Fposition allegations involving PSNI
OL,21,Fofficers and staff.
