OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FPolice said they had adopted
OL,8,Frecommendations made, or were working
OL,9,Fto put them in place.
OL,11,FThe watchdog report raises concerns
OL,12,Fover delays in case progression as
OL,13,Fwell as how abuse of position cases
OL,14,Fare defined and has made a number of
OL,15,Frecommendations.
OL,17,FThe chief inspector has also called on
OL,18,Fthe Department of Justice to expedite
OL,19,Fa legislative amendment to ensure
OL,20,Fswifter disciplinary action can be
OL,21,Ftaken by the PSNI.
