OL,7,FMs Durkin said: "When a person
OL,8,Fentrusted with the powers of a police
OL,9,Fofficer or a civilian member of staff
OL,10,Femployed by the PSNI abuses their
OL,11,Fposition or authority for their own or
OL,12,Fsomeone else's gain or disadvantage,
OL,13,Fit not only harms victims, it damages
OL,14,Fconfidence in policing and lets us all
OL,15,Fdown.
