OL,4,Caccused of using position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"Abuse of position can occur in many
OL,8,Fways, from unlawfully using a police
OL,9,Fcomputer, accessing police records or
OL,10,Fthe misuse of a police-issue mobile
OL,11,Fphone or device, to situations where
OL,12,Fsomeone abuses their position or
OL,13,Fauthority for financial gain or a
OL,14,Fsexual purpose.
OL,16,F"It is a form of corruption."
