OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"We sometimes think of police
OL,8,Fcorruption as horrific, high-profile
OL,9,Fcrimes that happen elsewhere, but as
OL,10,Frecent court convictions have proven,
OL,11,Fit happens here in our community.
OL,13,F"In July 2024, the OPONI had 19 active
OL,14,Finvestigations into cases of abuse of
OL,15,Fposition for sexual purposes ` the
OL,16,Fhighest number of such cases to date."
