OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,FShe added: "When abuse of position
OL,8,Foccurs, no matter what shape it takes,
OL,9,Fcomplaints and referrals require a
OL,10,Frobust response, including
OL,11,Findependent, effective investigation
OL,12,Fand timely appropriate outcomes, to
OL,13,Fmaintain public trust and confidence
OL,14,Fin the PSNI and to act as a deterrent
OL,15,Fto others."
OL,17,FThe report identified areas for
OL,18,Fimprovement and made five strategic
OL,19,Fand six operational recommendations.
