OL,4,Caccused of using position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"Inspectors recommend that in the next
OL,8,Fsix months a definition of abuse of
OL,9,Fposition should be developed by the
OL,10,FOPONI together with an abuse of
OL,11,Fposition strategy which includes
OL,12,Fmonitoring outcomes and a timeframe
OL,13,Ffor delivery," said Ms Durkin.
OL,15,FShe also said that inspection
OL,16,Ffieldwork found vacancies at
OL,17,Finvestigating officer level in the
OL,18,FOPONI, which were also contributing to
OL,19,Fdelays in case progression.
