OL,7,FMs Durkin said: "While all of these
OL,8,Fvictims now formed part of the Police
OL,9,FOmbudsman's investigations, we have
OL,10,Frecommended the PSNI's Professional
OL,11,FStandards Department work with the
OL,12,FOPONI over the next three months to
OL,13,Festablish if additional training is
OL,14,Fneeded for police officers regarding
OL,15,Fabuse of position for a sexual
OL,16,Fpurpose, or, if a lack of clarity
OL,17,Faround case referral or recording was
OL,18,Fcontributing to this inconsistency.
