OL,3,C'It's a form of corruption': Police
OL,4,Caccused of using position for sexual
OL,5,Cpurpose
OL,7,F"Inspectors also recommended the PSNI
OL,8,Fshould review and amend its guidance
OL,9,Ffor staff on maintaining professional
OL,10,Fboundaries between the police and
OL,11,Fmembers of the public, so all cases of
OL,12,Fabuse of position for a sexual purpose
OL,13,Fwill be referred by them to the OPONI
OL,14,Fand recent learning in this area is
OL,15,Fcaptured."
OL,17,FResponding to the report, PSNI Deputy
OL,18,FChief Constable Bobby Singleton said
OL,19,Fall of its recommendations are already
OL,20,Feither in place or are currently being
OL,21,Fprogressed.
