OL,7,FHe said: "The abuse of position by a
OL,8,Fserving police officer or staff member
OL,9,Fis totally unacceptable, it is not and
OL,10,Fwill not be tolerated.
OL,12,F"Last year, we reissued a service-wide
OL,13,Fstatement of intent, which made
OL,14,Fexplicit once again that there will be
OL,15,Fno tolerance for police officers and
OL,16,Fpolice staff who abuse their power.
OL,18,F"We will continue to work with OPONI
OL,19,Fand other criminal justice partners to
OL,20,Fcrack down on this type of behaviour
OL,21,Fwithin our organisation."
